        "text_dX9H3D": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>One in four adults over the age of 45 experiences frequent foot discomfort which can reduce physical activity and potentially contribute to poor mental health. Many older adults experience foot pain and therefore become less active and mobile. One way to prevent foot pain and muscle weakness from occurring is to stay active. But in order to be active, one must first be comfortable on his/her feet.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-sm",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.6,
            "text_letter_spacing": 0,
